   "source": [
    "# 9.5 推理时计算扩展 (Test-Time Compute)\n",
    "\n",
    "> 🕐 预估学习时间：40分钟\n",
    "\n",
    "2024-2025 年最重要的趋势：通过在推理阶段投入更多计算来显著提升输出质量。代表模型：OpenAI o1/o3、DeepSeek-R1。\n",
    "\n",
    "本节涵盖：\n",
    "- Chain-of-Thought 推理\n",
    "- Self-Consistency（多次采样投票）\n",
    "- Best-of-N 采样\n",
    "- 推理时搜索（Tree Search / Beam Search）\n",
    "- 验证器引导的推理\n",
    "- 计算最优分配策略"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Chain-of-Thought 推理\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心思想**：让模型在输出最终答案前先生成逐步推理过程，将复杂问题分解为易处理的子步骤。\n",
    "\n",
    "**为什么 CoT 有效**：\n",
    "- 将隐性推理外部化，每个步骤都有明确的计算\n",
    "- 中间步骤提供更多"思考时间"，等价于更深的前向传播\n",
    "- 自回归生成的每一步都是一次计算，CoT 增加了总计算量\n",
    "- 对于需要多步推理的任务（数学、逻辑），CoT 几乎总是提升准确率\n",
    "\n",
    "**OpenAI o1 的创新**：\n",
    "- 将 CoT 从 prompt 技巧内化为模型的默认行为\n",
    "- 使用强化学习训练模型生成更长的内部推理链\n",
    "- 推理链对用户隐藏，仅输出最终答案"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "import math\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class SimpleReasoningModel(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, d_model=64, vocab_size=50):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.embed = nn.Embedding(vocab_size, d_model)\n",
    "        self.transformer = nn.TransformerEncoder(\n",
    "            nn.TransformerEncoderLayer(d_model, 4, 128, batch_first=True), 2\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        self.lm_head = nn.Linear(d_model, vocab_size)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        h = self.embed(x)\n",
    "        h = self.transformer(h)\n",
    "        return self.lm_head(h)\n",
    "\n",
    "def generate_with_cot(model, prompt, max_cot_steps=4, max_answer_steps=2):\n",
    "    B = prompt.shape[0]\n",
    "    generated = prompt.clone()\n",
    "    cot_tokens = []\n",
    "\n",
    "    for step in range(max_cot_steps):\n",
    "        logits = model(generated)\n",
    "        next_token = logits[:, -1, :].argmax(dim=-1)\n",
    "        cot_tokens.append(next_token)\n",
    "        generated = torch.cat([generated, next_token.unsqueeze(1)], dim=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    answer_tokens = []\n",
    "    for step in range(max_answer_steps):\n",
    "        logits = model(generated)\n",
    "        next_token = logits[:, -1, :].argmax(dim=-1)\n",
    "        answer_tokens.append(next_token)\n",
    "        generated = torch.cat([generated, next_token.unsqueeze(1)], dim=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return generated, cot_tokens, answer_tokens\n",
    "\n",
    "def generate_direct(model, prompt, max_steps=2):\n",
    "    generated = prompt.clone()\n",
    "    answer_tokens = []\n",
    "    for _ in range(max_steps):\n",
    "        logits = model(generated)\n",
    "        next_token = logits[:, -1, :].argmax(dim=-1)\n",
    "        answer_tokens.append(next_token)\n",
    "        generated = torch.cat([generated, next_token.unsqueeze(1)], dim=1)\n",
    "    return generated, answer_tokens\n",
    "\n",
    "model = SimpleReasoningModel()\n",
    "prompt = torch.randint(0, 50, (1, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "out_cot, cot_tokens, ans_cot = generate_with_cot(model, prompt)\n",
    "out_direct, ans_direct = generate_direct(model, prompt)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Chain-of-Thought vs Direct Answer ===')\n",
    "print(f'Prompt tokens: {prompt.shape[1]}')\n",
    "print(f'\\nCoT generation:')\n",
    "print(f'  CoT steps: {len(cot_tokens)} (internal reasoning)')\n",
    "print(f'  Answer steps: {len(ans_cot)}')\n",
    "print(f'  Total compute: {len(cot_tokens) + len(ans_cot)} forward passes')\n",
    "print(f'\\nDirect generation:')\n",
    "print(f'  Answer steps: {len(ans_direct)}')\n",
    "print(f'  Total compute: {len(ans_direct)} forward passes')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: CoT uses more test-time compute (more forward passes).')\n",
    "print(f'Each extra step is a chance to refine reasoning.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Self-Consistency（自一致性）\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心思想**：对同一问题多次采样生成多条 CoT 推理路径，选择出现频率最高的答案。\n",
    "\n",
    "**原理**：\n",
    "- 单次推理可能随机出错，多条路径的共识更可靠\n",
    "- 等价于在推理路径空间中进行"投票"\n",
    "- 计算量：N 次采样 × CoT 推理\n",
    "- 实践表明 N=5~10 时收益最大\n",
    "\n",
    "**适用场景**：\n",
    "- 数学题：不同推理路径可能得到不同答案，多数投票选正确答案\n",
    "- 代码生成：多次生成后通过测试用例验证\n",
    "- 知识问答：多条推理链中一致的答案更可信"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "from collections import Counter\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "def self_consistency_sampling(model, prompt, n_samples=5, cot_steps=3, ans_steps=1):\n",
    "    all_answers = []\n",
    "    all_trajectories = []\n",
    "\n",
    "    for s in range(n_samples):\n",
    "        torch.manual_seed(42 + s)\n",
    "        generated, cot_tokens, ans_tokens = generate_with_cot(\n",
    "            model, prompt, max_cot_steps=cot_steps, max_answer_steps=ans_steps\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        answer_tuple = tuple(t.item() for t in ans_tokens)\n",
    "        all_answers.append(answer_tuple)\n",
    "        all_trajectories.append((cot_tokens, ans_tokens))\n",
    "\n",
    "    answer_counts = Counter(all_answers)\n",
    "    most_common_answer, count = answer_counts.most_common(1)[0]\n",
    "    confidence = count / n_samples\n",
    "\n",
    "    return most_common_answer, confidence, all_answers, answer_counts\n",
    "\n",
    "model = SimpleReasoningModel()\n",
    "prompt = torch.randint(0, 50, (1, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "answer, confidence, all_answers, counts = self_consistency_sampling(\n",
    "    model, prompt, n_samples=5\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Self-Consistency Sampling ===')\n",
    "print(f'Samples: 5 independent CoT runs')\n",
    "print(f'\\nAnswer distribution:')\n",
    "for ans, count in counts.most_common():\n",
    "    bar = '█' * count\n",
    "    print(f'  {ans}: {count}/5 {bar}')\n",
    "print(f'\\nFinal answer: {answer} (confidence: {confidence:.0%})')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: Majority voting over multiple reasoning paths.')\n",
    "print(f'Self-consistency turns compute into accuracy.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Best-of-N 采样\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心思想**：生成 N 个候选答案，用验证器（Verifier）选出最优的一个。\n",
    "\n",
    "**与 Self-Consistency 的区别**：\n",
    "- Self-Consistency：用多数投票选择答案，适合离散答案\n",
    "- Best-of-N：用评分函数选最优，适合连续质量评价\n",
    "\n",
    "**OpenAI o1 使用 Best-of-N + PRM（过程奖励模型）**：\n",
    "- 对每个推理步骤打分\n",
    "- 选择步骤分累积最高的完整推理链\n",
    "- 这本质上是一种推理时的搜索策略"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class Verifier(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, d_model=64):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.net = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Linear(d_model, 128), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(128, 1)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.net(x.mean(dim=1)).squeeze(-1)\n",
    "\n",
    "def best_of_n(model, verifier, prompt, n=5, max_steps=3):\n",
    "    best_score = -float('inf')\n",
    "    best_output = None\n",
    "    all_scores = []\n",
    "\n",
    "    for i in range(n):\n",
    "        generated = prompt.clone()\n",
    "        for _ in range(max_steps):\n",
    "            logits = model(generated)\n",
    "            probs = F.softmax(logits[:, -1, :], dim=-1)\n",
    "            next_token = torch.multinomial(probs, 1)\n",
    "            generated = torch.cat([generated, next_token], dim=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "        score = verifier(generated.float()).item()\n",
    "        all_scores.append(score)\n",
    "\n",
    "        if score > best_score:\n",
    "            best_score = score\n",
    "            best_output = generated\n",
    "\n",
    "    return best_output, best_score, all_scores\n",
    "\n",
    "model = SimpleReasoningModel()\n",
    "verifier = Verifier(d_model=64)\n",
    "prompt = torch.randint(0, 50, (1, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "best_out, best_score, all_scores = best_of_n(model, verifier, prompt, n=5)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Best-of-N Sampling ===')\n",
    "for i, score in enumerate(all_scores):\n",
    "    marker = ' ← BEST' if score == best_score else ''\n",
    "    print(f'  Sample {i+1}: score={score:.3f}{marker}')\n",
    "print(f'\\nBest score: {best_score:.3f}')\n",
    "print(f'Average score: {sum(all_scores)/len(all_scores):.3f}')\n",
    "print(f'Gain over average: {(best_score - sum(all_scores)/len(all_scores)):.3f}')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: Best-of-N uses a verifier to select the top candidate.')\n",
    "print(f'Quality improves with √N (diminishing returns).')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 推理时搜索（Tree Search）\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心思想**：将推理过程建模为搜索问题，在推理步骤空间中系统性地搜索最优路径。\n",
    "\n",
    "**Tree of Thoughts (ToT)**：\n",
    "- 每个节点是一个推理状态\n",
    "- BFS/DFS 探索多条推理分支\n",
    "- 使用评估函数剪枝低质量分支\n",
    "\n",
    "**Beam Search 推理**：\n",
    "- 每步保留 Top-K 个最佳推理状态\n",
    "- 在推理链级别而非 token 级别做 beam search\n",
    "- K 越大，搜索越广，计算越多\n",
    "\n",
    "**OpenAI o1 的隐式搜索**：\n",
    "- 不再显式编程搜索算法\n",
    "- 通过 RL 训练让模型学会在内部进行"思维搜索"\n",
    "- 模型自动生成、评估、修正多条推理路径"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import heapq\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class ReasoningNode:\n",
    "    def __init__(self, state, score, depth, parent=None):\n",
    "        self.state = state\n",
    "        self.score = score\n",
    "        self.depth = depth\n",
    "        self.parent = parent\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __lt__(self, other):\n",
    "        return self.score > other.score\n",
    "\n",
    "def beam_search_reasoning(model, verifier, prompt, beam_width=3, max_depth=4):\n",
    "    root = ReasoningNode(prompt.clone(), 0.0, 0)\n",
    "    beam = [root]\n",
    "\n",
    "    for depth in range(max_depth):\n",
    "        candidates = []\n",
    "\n",
    "        for node in beam:\n",
    "            for b in range(beam_width):\n",
    "                logits = model(node.state)\n",
    "                probs = F.softmax(logits[:, -1, :], dim=-1)\n",
    "                next_token = torch.multinomial(probs, 1)\n",
    "                new_state = torch.cat([node.state, next_token], dim=1)\n",
    "                step_score = verifier(new_state.float()).item()\n",
    "                total_score = node.score + step_score\n",
    "                child = ReasoningNode(new_state, total_score, depth + 1, node)\n",
    "                candidates.append(child)\n",
    "\n",
    "        beam = heapq.nlargest(beam_width, candidates, key=lambda x: x.score)\n",
    "\n",
    "    best_node = beam[0]\n",
    "    path = []\n",
    "    node = best_node\n",
    "    while node.parent:\n",
    "        path.append(node.state.shape[1] - node.parent.state.shape[1])\n",
    "        node = node.parent\n",
    "\n",
    "    return best_node, path[::-1]\n",
    "\n",
    "model = SimpleReasoningModel()\n",
    "verifier = Verifier(d_model=64)\n",
    "prompt = torch.randint(0, 50, (1, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "best_node, path = beam_search_reasoning(model, verifier, prompt, beam_width=3, max_depth=4)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Beam Search Reasoning ===')\n",
    "print(f'Beam width: 3, Max depth: 4')\n",
    "print(f'Best score: {best_node.score:.3f}')\n",
    "print(f'Output length: {best_node.state.shape[1]}')\n",
    "print(f'Tokens per step: {path}')\n",
    "\n",
    "total_nodes = sum(3 ** d for d in range(5))\n",
    "print(f'\\nExplored nodes: up to {total_nodes} (beam prunes most)')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: Beam search systematically explores reasoning paths.')\n",
    "print(f'Beam width controls the compute-vs-accuracy trade-off.')"
   ]
  },
