    "## 5. 计算最优分配策略\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心问题**：给定推理计算预算，如何在各种策略间最优分配？\n",
    "\n",
    "**策略对比**：\n",
    "\n",
    "| 策略 | 计算量 | 准确率增益 | 适用场景 |\n",
    "|------|--------|------------|----------|\n",
    "| CoT | 2-5× | 中等 | 所有推理任务 |\n",
    "| Self-Consistency (N=5) | 5× | 高 | 离散答案任务 |\n",
    "| Best-of-N (N=10) | 10× | 高 | 有验证器的任务 |\n",
    "| Beam Search (K=5) | ~25× | 很高 | 可逐步验证的任务 |\n",
    "| 混合策略 | 可变 | 最优 | 生产环境 |\n",
    "\n",
    "**实用建议**：\n",
    "- 先尝试 CoT（0 额外训练成本）\n",
    "- 有验证器就加 Best-of-N\n",
    "- 数学/代码任务优先 Self-Consistency\n",
    "- 最高质量需求用 Beam Search 或训练推理模型"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def compute_scaling_law(n_samples_list=[1, 3, 5, 10, 20, 50]):\n",
    "    single_shot_accuracy = 0.60\n",
    "    error_rate = 1 - single_shot_accuracy\n",
    "\n",
    "    print('=== Compute vs Accuracy Trade-off ===')\n",
    "    print(f'Single-shot accuracy: {single_shot_accuracy:.0%}')\n",
    "    print(f'\\n{\"Samples\":>8} {\"Compute\":>8} {\"Maj-Vote Acc\":>14} {\"Best-of-N Acc\":>14}')\n",
    "    print('-' * 48)\n",
    "\n",
    "    for n in n_samples_list:\n",
    "        maj_vote_acc = 0\n",
    "        for k in range(n // 2 + 1, n + 1):\n",
    "            from math import comb\n",
    "            maj_vote_acc += comb(n, k) * (single_shot_accuracy ** k) * (error_rate ** (n - k))\n",
    "\n",
    "        best_of_n_acc = 1 - (error_rate ** n)\n",
    "\n",
    "        print(f'{n:>8} {n:>8}× {maj_vote_acc:>13.1%} {best_of_n_acc:>13.1%}')\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(f'\\nKey: Majority voting saturates faster than Best-of-N.')\n",
    "    print(f'Best-of-N with perfect verifier approaches 100% as N→∞.')\n",
    "\n",
    "compute_scaling_law()"
   ]
  },
